  "detailed_description": "<br>Unlimited Fight is born out of what is a new story created by the enthusiasm of young fighting game lovers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/308b3ea626bbd79a4b108607f82a54d0.poster.avif?t=1772905067\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/308b3ea626bbd79a4b108607f82a54d0.webm?t=1772905067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/308b3ea626bbd79a4b108607f82a54d0.mp4?t=1772905067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Become a street fighter, a ninja, a soldier, a muay thai fighter, a wrestler, and more in this incredible world.<br>Try one of these fighting styles and enter the Unlimited Fighting tournament one of the iconic characters, each with a different motivation to participate in that tournament, and face friends locally.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/1b1d7de07639b0755475a1631d975900.poster.avif?t=1772905067\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/1b1d7de07639b0755475a1631d975900.webm?t=1772905067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/1b1d7de07639b0755475a1631d975900.mp4?t=1772905067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<br>Unlimited Fight is born out of what is a new story created by the enthusiasm of young fighting game lovers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/308b3ea626bbd79a4b108607f82a54d0.poster.avif?t=1772905067\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/308b3ea626bbd79a4b108607f82a54d0.webm?t=1772905067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/308b3ea626bbd79a4b108607f82a54d0.mp4?t=1772905067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Become a street fighter, a ninja, a soldier, a muay thai fighter, a wrestler, and more in this incredible world.<br>Try one of these fighting styles and enter the Unlimited Fighting tournament one of the iconic characters, each with a different motivation to participate in that tournament, and face friends locally.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/1b1d7de07639b0755475a1631d975900.poster.avif?t=1772905067\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/1b1d7de07639b0755475a1631d975900.webm?t=1772905067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469330/extras/1b1d7de07639b0755475a1631d975900.mp4?t=1772905067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
